beer.beer_description: If you're reading this, you've made it! It's Christmas and boy does your mouth deserve this vacation. As one of the first in Australia to brew a Cold IPA, we had to brew another! Let this light malt base, painted with a plethora of hops reward your tastebuds. Starting with an aromatic intensity and solid bitterness yet finishing crisp and clean. You are left with a beautiful bright beer that will surely put you on the nice list.
